                    </div>
                    <span>This book is basically the MAN pages included with Linux, and all versions of UNIX. But it's in a form that can be held and browsed through making it much more usable and convenient.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">This is the reference you need</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>5</span>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Helpful: </span>
